      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be demonstrated to be representative of the COU geometry, flow regime, and blood analogue at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Validation used the FDA generic centrifugal pump with bovine blood; relevance to patient-specific VAD geometries and human blood rheology is asserted without formal similarity analysis, limiting achieved level to 2."
