      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test sample characterization must include statistical representation of the sample population and traceability at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Blood sample provenance, storage conditions, and population representativeness are not documented. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level defaulted to 1."
